      "representation": "view",
      "value": "<h3 id=\"HippieDragonPosing-Posing\">Posing</h3><p>After completing texturing work, I came back to Zbrush to pose my model. As a last step I had to add and subtract a few wrinkles and folds here and there to match with the new pose. I also added some asymmetry and &quot;flow&quot; to the leaves and petals. For this entire process, I decided to use layering in ZBrush as it involved a little trial and error. I used separate layers for the pose and the new wrinkles and the sculpting on the leaves and petals.</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"image8.jpg\" width=\"760\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/657391753/image8.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1762592666242&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=760&amp;height=472\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/657391753/image8.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1762592666242&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"1080\" data-width=\"1738\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"657228111\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"image8.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"657391753\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"25181aaa-583b-4139-a204-c7cfca1a87bb\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/657391753/image8.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1762592666242&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=1520&amp;height=944 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/657391753/image8.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1762592666242&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=760&amp;height=472 1x\">